### Register user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ryan User",
  "email": "ryan@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}


### Login user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ryan@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}


### Login user with wrong password
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ryan@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

