### Get all exercises
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exercises


### Create exercise: Bench Press
POST http://localhost:3000/api/exercises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bench Press",
  "muscleGroup": "chest",
  "equipment": "barbell"
}


### Create exercise: Shoulder Press
POST http://localhost:3000/api/exercises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Shoulder Press",
  "muscleGroup": "shoulders",
  "equipment": "dumbbell"
}


### Get exercise by id: Bench Press
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exercises/6a0456b1d0d4e48ffe7650b4

### Update exercise: Bench Press
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/exercises/6a0456b1d0d4e48ffe7650b4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bench Press",
  "muscleGroup": "chest",
  "equipment": "barbell"
}


